      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "イヤです～！　寒いです～！\n対策しても寒過ぎます～～！！",
      "startTime": 14.5643781662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "カイロがなければ即引き返してました……！\nカイロ様々ですよ……！",
      "startTime": 20.2977114995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきまでの威勢はどうしたんだ？\nまぁ、ゆっくりでも進んでるからいいけど",
      "startTime": 25.5333345413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "こころに外に出てほしいという\n{user}さんたってのお願いですからね～",
      "startTime": 31.3534259796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、さすがにそろそろ……\nあっ、あそこのかまくらで一休みしていきましょう！",
      "startTime": 38.3867557526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "街中にかまくら？　……本当だ。観光客向けに\n作ったみたいだな。中でおしるこを売ってるのか",
      "startTime": 48.2333238602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "このままでは二人とも\n心身ともに冷え切って遭難してしまいます……！",
      "startTime": 54.4420545578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "おしるこを飲まない限り\nこころは一歩も動けません～！",
      "startTime": 60.1420545578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。練習の時間まで余裕があるし、寄って行こう",
      "startTime": 62.7635725657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　いいんですか？",
      "startTime": 67.0329765002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "冗談っぽく言ってるけど、本当に辛いんだろ？",
      "startTime": 68.8900965769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにはバレちゃいますね\nごめんなさい、寄り道させちゃって",
      "startTime": 75.7678307693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、暖を取りながら、少しずつ進めば\nいつの日かスタジオに辿り着けるはずです……！",
      "startTime": 81.6344984532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、時間までに辿り着いてもらわないと困るけどな",
      "startTime": 84.6639298995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "startTime": 89.217265153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ごちそうさまでした……っと\nやれやれ、随分な寄り道になったな",
      "startTime": 94.8666515987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "もうお腹一杯です……これ以上何も入りません……",
      "startTime": 98.1704977592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃそうだ。かまくらでおしるこを飲んだ後\nさらにラーメンまで食べたんだから",
      "startTime": 106.6666531246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "暖を取りながらここまで来ましたけど\nもう温かいものはこれ以上食べられません～",
      "startTime": 112.4471539339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "スタジオまで後少しだ。頑張れないか？",
      "startTime": 116.4407490175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……でも、それまでこころの体力がもつでしょうか\n……あれ？",
      "startTime": 126.2666717848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "……あの子達、リズノワのこと、話してますね\nこころ達のファン……でしょうか？",
      "startTime": 131.3000086786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "……あの子達の話、聞きました？\nバイト代とお小遣いを貯めてチケットを手に入れたって",
      "startTime": 139.0000086786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirが北海道に来るのは初めてだからな\n俺達が思っている以上に、楽しみにしてくれてるんだな",
      "startTime": 147.1999803544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "これが、あの子達にとって\n初めてのリズノワのライブになるんですね……",
      "startTime": 153.5983855885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "私達にとっての北海道は、数あるツアー先の一つだけど\n北海道の人達にとっては、初めてで、一度きりの……",
      "startTime": 162.9650522551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、{user}さん、そろそろ行きませんか？",
      "startTime": 169.2086399318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "今日は沢山食べちゃったから\n一杯体を動かして、カロリーを消費しないと～",
      "startTime": 174.9650471689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
